'''易卜拉欣·阿瓦德·易卜拉欣·阿里·穆罕默德·巴德里·薩瑪拉·阿布·貝克爾·巴格達迪'''（{{lang-ar|إبراهيم عواد إبراهيم علي محمد البدري السامرائي أبو بكر البغدادي}}；{{bd|1971年|7月28日|2019年|10月27日|catIdx=Bagdadi, Abu Bakr}}），又被称作'''阿布·貝克爾·巴格達迪'''（{{rtl-lang|ar|أبو بكر البغدادي}}）、'''易卜拉欣[[哈里發|哈里發]]'''（{{rtl-lang|ar|خَلِيفَةُ إِبْرَاهِيم}}）或'''阿布·杜阿'''（{{rtl-lang|ar|أبو دعاء}}）<ref name="announcement">{{cite web |url= http://www.webcitation.org/62Hxw9AqD |title= Wanted: Abu Du’a; Up to $10 Million |publisher= Rewards for Justice |date=  |accessdate= 2011-10-08 |language= en |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150128074353/http://www.webcitation.org/62Hxw9AqD |archive-date= 2015-01-28 |dead-url= no }}</ref>，[[伊斯蘭神學|伊斯蘭神學]]學者，極端[[伊斯蘭恐怖主義|伊斯蘭恐怖主義]]組織“[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]”（ISIS）的[[最高領導人|最高領導人]]，并自封为“伊斯兰国”的“[[哈里发|哈里发]]”<ref name="names">{{cite web |url= http://www.state.gov/r/pa/prs/ps/2014/05/226067.htm |title= Terrorist Designations of Groups Operating in Syria |publisher= U.S. Department   of State |date= 2014-05-14 |accessdate= 2014-06-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140518024433/http://www.state.gov/r/pa/prs/ps/2014/05/226067.htm |archive-date= 2014-05-18 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。被欧美和中东大部分国家列为頭號[[恐怖分子|恐怖分子]]。

伊斯蘭國在2013年4月8日通过巴格达迪起草的一份声明宣布成立。他成功地组建了伊斯兰国，为[[蓋達組織|蓋達組織]]的分支<ref name="memri">{{cite web|url=http://www.memri.org/report/en/0/0/0/0/0/0/7119.htm|title=ISI Confirms That Jabhat Al-Nusra Is Its Extension in Syria, Declares 'Islamic State of Iraq And Al-Sham' As New Name of Merged Group|publisher=Memri|date=2013-04-08|accessdate=2014-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006085808/http://www.memri.org/report/en/0/0/0/0/0/0/7119.htm|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，之后其脱离蓋達組織自立。2011年10月4日[[美国政府|美国政府]]把他列为全球首级恐怖分子并悬赏1,000万美元击毙或抓捕<ref name="state">{{cite web |url= http://www.webcitation.org/62HxbVjBF |title= Terrorist Designation of Ibrahim Awwad Ibrahim Ali al-Badri |publisher= United States Department of State |date= 2011-10-04 |accessdate= 2011-10-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150128074353/http://www.webcitation.org/62HxbVjBF |archive-date= 2015-01-28 |dead-url= no }}</ref>，其悬赏金仅次于蓋達组织首领[[艾曼·扎瓦希里|艾曼·扎瓦希里]]（2,500万美元）<ref name="ayman">{{cite web |url= http://www.webcitation.org/62I0kqNH3 |title= IRAQ: U.S. offers $10-million reward for Al Qaeda in Iraq leader |publisher= Los Angeles Times |date= 2011-10-07 |accessdate= 2011-10-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140223161238/http://www.webcitation.org/62I0kqNH3 |archive-date= 2014-02-23 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

2014年6月29日「伊斯兰国」宣佈建國，巴格达迪自封為哈里發<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2014/06-30/6332849.shtml |title=伊拉克叛军重建“伊斯兰帝国”挑战“基地”组织 |publisher=中新網 |date=2014-06-30 |access-date=2014-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140703191335/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2014/06-30/6332849.shtml |archive-date=2014-07-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>並改用本名易卜拉欣，自稱「'''易卜拉欣哈里發'''」。然而他的稱號不受大部分[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]承認<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.cnyes.com/Content%2F20140701%2Fkiwj856aneaf2.shtml|title=ISIL立伊斯蘭國 號召穆斯林效忠巴格達迪 挑戰蓋達地位|publisher=鉅亨網|date=2014-07-01|access-date=2014-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714234854/http://news.cnyes.com/Content%2F20140701%2Fkiwj856aneaf2.shtml|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[塔利班|塔利班]]亦不承认其“哈里发”的地位，称他为“伪哈里发”<ref>{{cite web| title =Taliban leader: allegiance to ISIS 'haram'| url =http://rudaw.net/english/middleeast/130420151| website =Rudaw| date =2015-04-13| accessdate =2015-07-31| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150713102756/http://rudaw.net/english/middleeast/130420151| archive-date =2015-07-13| dead-url =yes}}</ref>。参加行动的三角洲队员跟相关人员媒体屡次传出巴格达迪被炸死或炸伤的消息，但均未获得证实。2019年10月27日，美國[[福斯新聞|福斯新聞]]快訊報導，巴格達迪死於美方在[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]西北部城市[[伊德利卜|伊德利卜]]的[[巴里沙突袭|行動]]中<ref name=dead>{{Cite web|title=伊斯蘭國領袖傳身亡！　美媒：死於美軍在敘利亞的行動中|url=https://www.ettoday.net/news/20191027/1566274.htm|publisher=ETtoday|date=2019-10-27|accessdate=2019-10-27|archive-date=2019-10-27|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191027042446/https://www.ettoday.net/news/20191027/1566274.htm}}</ref>，隨後[[美國政府|美國政府]]證實此訊息<ref name=dead2>{{Cite web|title=川普重大宣布！美軍擊斃IS首領巴格達迪|url=https://www.ettoday.net/news/20191027/1566484.htm|publisher=ETtoday|date=2019-10-27|accessdate=2019-10-27|archive-date=2019-10-27|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191027134139/https://www.ettoday.net/news/20191027/1566484.htm}}</ref><ref name=dead3>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201910275007.aspx |title=川普：美軍突襲敘利亞 伊斯蘭國首腦喪生[影] |publisher=中央社 |date=2019-10-27 |accessdate=2019-10-27 |archive-date=2019-10-27 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191027134616/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201910275007.aspx }}</ref>。不久伊斯蘭國亦承認巴格達迪之死，並宣布新任哈里發由[[阿布·易卜拉欣·哈希米·库雷希|阿布·易卜拉欣·哈希米·库雷希]]接任。

== 生平== 
出生于[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]的[[萨迈拉|萨迈拉]]附近<ref name = "Graun bio">{{Cite news |last = Chulov |first = Martin |date = 2014-07-06 |title = Abu Bakr al-Baghdadi emerges from shadows to rally Islamist followers |url = http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jul/06/abu-bakr-al-baghdadi-isis |work = [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |accessdate = 2014-07-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140719214932/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jul/06/abu-bakr-al-baghdadi-isis |archive-date = 2014-07-19 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。曾经就读于伊拉克郊区[[阿宰米耶伊斯兰学大学|阿宰米耶伊斯兰学大学]]，获伊斯兰学硕士学位和博士学位。

2003年[[伊拉克战争|美国入侵伊拉克]]的时候，他在一个清真寺当[[阿訇|阿訇]]<ref name="Abu">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-27801676|title=Profile: Abu Bakr al-Baghdadi|publisher=BBC News|date=2014-07-05|accessdate=2014-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140615123734/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-27801676|archive-date=2014-06-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name = "Graun bio"/>。根据[[美国国防部|美国国防部]]记录，巴格达迪在美国入侵伊拉克期间于2004年2月被美军以{{en-link|平民被拘留者|Civilian Internee}}的身分扣留拘押在{{en-link|布卡营|Camp Bucca}}；2004年12月初因为没有审查出他有犯罪前科被关押的记录，他被“无条件释放”<ref name = "fact check">{{cite web |date = 2014-06-19 |title = Fox's Pirro: Obama set ISIS leader free in 2009 |url = http://www.politifact.com/punditfact/statements/2014/jun/19/jeanine-pirro/foxs-pirro-obama-set-isis-leader-free-2009/ |publisher = ''[[Tampa_Bay_Times|Tampa Bay Times]]'' |work = [[PolitiFact.com|PolitiFact.com]] |accessdate = 2014-06-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140721120617/http://www.politifact.com/punditfact/statements/2014/jun/19/jeanine-pirro/foxs-pirro-obama-set-isis-leader-free-2009/ |archive-date = 2014-07-21 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2010年一位前[[萨达姆|萨达姆]]军队的将军将巴格达迪介绍给刚刚失去首脑（{{en-link|阿布·奧馬爾·巴格達迪|Abu Abdullah al-Rashid al-Baghdadi}}、[[阿布·艾尤卜·马斯里|阿布·艾尤卜·马斯里]]）的伊拉克伊斯兰国（ISI）。2013年巴格达迪合并了伊拉克境内多个伊斯兰组织，成立伊拉克和沙姆伊斯蘭國（Islamic State of Iraq and al-Sham，简称ISIS）。

在[[阿拉伯之冬|阿拉伯之冬]]发生之后，伊拉克和沙姆伊斯蘭國的势力渐渐强大，逐渐占据了叙利亚和伊拉克的大量领土，以[[拉卡|拉卡]]为其“首都”。2014年6月29日巴格达迪宣布将“伊拉克和沙姆”字样舍去，直接称为“伊斯兰国”（The Islamic State，简称IS），巴格达迪也恢复自己的本名“易卜拉欣”，自称哈里发<ref>{{cite news|title=Key Free Syria Army rebel 'killed by Islamist group'|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-23283079|publisher=BBC|date=2013-07-12|access-date=2015-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151125211923/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-23283079|archive-date=2015-11-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=AlArabiya_9-4-2013>{{cite news|title=Al-Qaeda in Iraq confirms Syria's Nusra Front is part of its network|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/04/09/Al-Qaeda-in-Iraq-confirms-Syria-s-Nusra-Front-is-part-of-its-network.html|accessdate=2014-06-15|agency=Al Arabiya|date=2013-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160119055306/http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/04/09/Al-Qaeda-in-Iraq-confirms-Syria-s-Nusra-Front-is-part-of-its-network.html|archive-date=2016-01-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不过他的声称没有得到任何一个阿拉伯国家的承认，其他聖戰組織如阿爾蓋達及塔利班亦不承认其合法性。

===下落之謎===
巴格达迪曾数次被报导被炸死或炸伤，但均未获得证实。

2015年10月11日，伊拉克军方声称巴格达迪前往伊拉克[[安巴尔省|安巴尔省]]与叙利亚交界一带的卡尔巴拉镇参加“伊斯兰国”的高层会议，遭到伊拉克军队的空袭。不少高层官员被炸死，巴格达迪本人则生死不明<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.takefoto.cn/viewnews-560980.html |title=ISIS首领巴格达迪被炸 生死不明多名高层头目死亡 |access-date=2015-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222121753/http://www.takefoto.cn/viewnews-560980.html |archive-date=2015-12-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月11日又有报导称，巴格达迪被炸伤后被送往拉卡紧急治疗，脱离了生命危险。但因医疗设备不足，又被送往土耳其就医，并躲避了美国和伊拉克的情报人员，辗转来到利比亚的[[苏尔特|苏尔特]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20151211/46622723_0.shtml |title=IS领袖巴格达迪遭空袭受伤 赴土就医后逃往卡扎菲家乡 |access-date=2015-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151211093816/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20151211/46622723_0.shtml |archive-date=2015-12-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月27日巴格達迪發布一段談話錄音，揚言要對以色列發動攻擊<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.storm.mg/article/76874 | title = 聯軍攻勢猛烈 伊斯蘭國首領嗆聲「IS不會被嚇倒，以色列小心！」 | publisher = [[風傳媒|風傳媒]] | access-date = 2015-12-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151229171747/http://www.storm.mg/article/76874 | archive-date = 2015-12-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2016年6月14日，英国《[[每日镜报|每日镜报]]》报导巴格达迪可能于两天前在一次美军领导的空袭中於[[拉卡|拉卡]]重伤而亡，不过这一消息並未經美國官方證實。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/isis-leader-abu-bakr-al-8186324|title=ISIS leader Abu Bakr al-Baghdadi 'killed in US-led air strikes in Syria'|date=2016-06-14|publisher=mirror|access-date=2016-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160614131511/http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/isis-leader-abu-bakr-al-8186324|archive-date=2016-06-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年11月2日，“伊斯兰国”发表巴格达迪本人的音频，鼓舞“伊斯兰国”武装分子防御[[摩苏尔|摩苏尔]]，并宣称“伊斯兰国”应该同[[什叶派|什叶派]]、[[阿拉维派|阿拉维派]]做斗争，开始与沙特阿拉伯、土耳其以及更远的国家战斗，并要在利比亚制造更多烈士。<ref>Graeme Wood – [https://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2016/11/caliph-baghdadi-mosul-isis-iraq-syria/506567/ ''The ‘Caliph’ Speaks'' As ISIS faces defeat in Mosul, its leader breaks a long silence to urge a fight to the death] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2016/11/caliph-baghdadi-mosul-isis-iraq-syria/506567/ |date=20170204003933 }} [[The_Atlantic|The Atlantic]] Retrieved 2017-02-03</ref><ref>Ananya Roy  – [http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/isis-chief-abu-bakr-al-baghdadi-still-alive-isolated-pentagon-says-1598760 Isis chief Abu Bakr al-Baghdadi still alive but isolated, Pentagon says] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/isis-chief-abu-bakr-al-baghdadi-still-alive-isolated-pentagon-says-1598760 |date=20170509224406 }} [[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]] December 31, 2016 Retrieved 2017-02-03</ref>

2017年6月11日，叙利亚国家电视台宣称巴格达迪被美军炸死<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldtribune.com/syrian-media-claim-isis-leader-killed-in-artillery-strike/|title=Syrian media claim ISIS leader killed in artillery strike|date=2017-06-11|publisher=|accessdate=2017-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170717103508/http://www.worldtribune.com/syrian-media-claim-isis-leader-killed-in-artillery-strike/|archive-date=2017-07-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>ISIS leader Abu Bakr al-Baghdadi has reportedly been killed in Raqqa, Syria, [http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-4592694/Syrian-state-TV-claims-Abu-Bakr-al-Baghdadi-dead.html#ixzz4jgn7TCrv Daily mail online, 11 June 2017.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-4592694/Syrian-state-TV-claims-Abu-Bakr-al-Baghdadi-dead.html#ixzz4jgn7TCrv |date=20170713084601 }}</ref>。6月16日，俄罗斯媒体报导則称巴格达迪可能在俄空军于5月28日对[[拉卡|拉卡]]的一次空袭中身亡<ref>{{cite web|title=Russia Says It May Have Killed IS Leader Al-Baghdadi In Air Strike|url=https://www.rferl.org/a/russia-killed-al-baghdadi-islamic-state-syria/28558271.html|website=www.rferl.org|accessdate=2017-06-16|date=2017-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170627200035/https://www.rferl.org/a/russia-killed-al-baghdadi-islamic-state-syria/28558271.html|archive-date=2017-06-27|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Isachenkov|first1=Vladimir|title=Russia claims it has killed IS leader al-Baghdadi|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/russia-claims-killed-leader-al-baghdadi-48077729|website=ABC News|date=2017-06-16|accessdate=2017-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170630100016/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/russia-claims-killed-leader-al-baghdadi-48077729|archive-date=2017-06-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>；美国媒体对此表示怀疑，指出此报导缺乏独立证据<ref>{{cite web|title=White House casts doubt on Russia's claim it killed ISIS leader|url=http://www.politico.com/story/2017/06/16/is-isis-leader-abu-bakr-al-baghdadi-dead-239641|website=Politico|date=2017-06-16|accessdate=2017-06-16|6=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170720070715/http://www.politico.com/story/2017/06/16/is-isis-leader-abu-bakr-al-baghdadi-dead-239641|archive-date=2017-07-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月23日，俄国政治人物Viktor Ozerov宣称巴格达迪之死已经“100%确认”<ref>{{cite news |title=Baghdadi death near 100 percent certain: Interfax quotes Russian senator |work=Reuters |date=2017-06-23 |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-baghdadi-russia-idUSKBN19E0PI |access-date=2017-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714100205/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-baghdadi-russia-idUSKBN19E0PI |archive-date=2017-07-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。伊朗随后证实了俄方的说法，称巴格达迪死于一场空袭<ref>{{cite news |title=Iran Confirms Death of ISIS Leader al-Baghdadi |work=Iran Front Page |date=2017-06-29 |url=http://ifpnews.com/exclusive/iran-confirms-death-of-isis-leader-al-baghdadi/ |access-date=2017-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170709165509/http://ifpnews.com/exclusive/iran-confirms-death-of-isis-leader-al-baghdadi |archive-date=2017-07-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。6月29日，伊朗的官方媒体[[伊朗伊斯兰共和国通讯社|伊朗伊斯兰共和国通讯社]]发表文章，援引最高领袖[[哈梅内伊|哈梅内伊]]的话称巴格达迪“确定死亡”，但该通讯社随后更新了此文并删除了该句<ref>{{cite web |last=Hafezi |first=Parisa |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-baghdadi-iran-idUSKBN19K2S4 |title=Khamenei's representative says Islamic state's Baghdadi 'definitely dead': IRNA |date=2017-06-29 |publisher=Reuters |accessdate=2017-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170709061640/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-baghdadi-iran-idUSKBN19K2S4 |archive-date=2017-07-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年7月11日，伊拉克{{link-en|苏马里亚电视台|Al Sumaria}}在其网站上称，“伊斯兰国”在[[泰勒阿费尔|泰勒阿费尔]]发布简短声明称巴格达迪已经死亡<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2017-07/11/c_136435541.htm|title=IS confirms death of top leader al-Baghdadi|publisher=Xinhua News Agency|access-date=2017-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170722144412/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2017-07/11/c_136435541.htm|archive-date=2017-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20170712/51416862_0.shtml|title=IS承认巴格达迪死亡 该组织在摩苏尔统治被推翻|publisher=凤凰资讯|access-date=2017-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713104512/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20170712/51416862_0.shtml|archive-date=2019-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://tv.cntv.cn/video/C10336/8d6ceb44995a463c8d20698830ce87c8|title=伊媒：极端组织宣布巴格达迪死亡|author=央视网|date=2017-07-12|access-date=2017-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713104512/http://tv.cntv.cn/video/C10336/8d6ceb44995a463c8d20698830ce87c8|archive-date=2019-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{link-en|叙利亚人权观察组织|Syrian Observatory for Human Rights}}宣称其死亡为确切消息<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/abu-bakr-al-baghdadi-dead-isis-leader-killed-latest-news-updates-a7835271.html|title=Abu Bakr Al-Baghdadi: Isis leader killed, says Syrian Observatory for Human Rights|publisher=The Independent|access-date=2017-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714003304/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/abu-bakr-al-baghdadi-dead-isis-leader-killed-latest-news-updates-a7835271.html|archive-date=2017-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美国国防部表示正在尝试确认关于他死亡的最新报道<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2017/07/11/isis-leader-al-baghdadi-reported-dead-though-pentagon-cant-confirm.html|title=ISIS leader al-Baghdadi reported dead, though Pentagon can't confirm|publisher=Fox News|access-date=2017-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170712235317/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2017/07/11/isis-leader-al-baghdadi-reported-dead-though-pentagon-cant-confirm.html|archive-date=2017-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://tv.cntv.cn/video/C10336/52f57eb1d35a4de38fdd58877276a244|title=美国防部称暂无法证实巴格达迪死讯|author=央视网|date=2017-07-12|access-date=2017-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713104513/http://tv.cntv.cn/video/C10336/52f57eb1d35a4de38fdd58877276a244|archive-date=2019-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年12月，土耳其報紙《葉尼薩法克報》（Yeni Safak）報導稱，巴格達迪與其他7名IS核心人士在伊拉克遭到美軍生擒，被關押在敘利亞北部的一座美軍基地，但該消息並未被證實。

2018年8月22日，据[[美國之音|美國之音]]報導，“伊斯兰国”公布了据稱是巴格达迪的54分钟讲话。巴格达迪在讲话中祝贺[[宰牲節|宰牲節]]，敦促“伊斯兰国”的支持者不要放弃。他还对支持者说，正在崩溃的是美国，而不是“伊斯兰国”。除此之外，他還提到了美国与土耳其有关[[安德鲁·布伦森|安德鲁·布伦森]]牧师的争端，以及“伊斯兰国”与叙利亚武装的交战情况。美国军方和情报界官员并未确认讲话者是否是巴格达迪。<ref>[https://www.voachinese.com/a/isis-baghdadi-20180822/4540624.html 伊斯兰国组织头目沉默近一年后发声] {{Wayback|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/isis-baghdadi-20180822/4540624.html |date=20180823174138 }}.美國之音.</ref>

2019年4月29日，“伊斯兰国”旗下媒體《標竿網》（Al-Furqan Network）公布巴格達迪的影片，推估拍攝時間於4月11至15日<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8662/3784914%26ved%3D2ahUKEwjgw6mYmffhAhWMblAKHT61Cy0QFjABegQIAxAB%26usg%3DAOvVaw1P-yMrcMen6HvXvU39J1qk%26ampcf%3D1 |title=ISIS領袖「巴格達迪」現身：證明沒死，5年來的第一次亮相 |date=2019-04-30 |access-date=2019-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191027151837/https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8662/3784914%26ved%3D2ahUKEwjgw6mYmffhAhWMblAKHT61Cy0QFjABegQIAxAB%26usg%3DAOvVaw1P-yMrcMen6HvXvU39J1qk%26ampcf%3D1 |archive-date=2019-10-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。巴格達迪在影片中承認伊斯兰国在叙利亚战事受挫，威胁发动更多“报复行动”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-04/30/c_1124439558.htm |title=“伊斯兰国”发布威胁视频　疑似巴格达迪现身 |publisher=新華網 |date=2019-04-30 |accessdate=2019-10-27 |archive-date=2019-10-27 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191027144308/http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-04/30/c_1124439558.htm }}</ref>。

===自爆身亡===
{{main|巴里沙突袭}}
2019年10月27日，时任[[美國總統|美國總統]][[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]召開記者會宣佈巴格達迪死於美軍[[巴里沙突袭|空襲敘利亞伊德利卜的行動]]；當時巴格達迪帶著兩個孩子於地道中引爆[[自殺炸彈|自殺炸彈]]的背心身亡{{noteTag|最初川普宣布時說巴格達迪帶著三個孩子，同月30日[[美國中央司令部|美國中央司令部]]宣布時說巴格達迪帶著兩個孩子。}}，其兩名妻子則在交火中身亡。<ref name=dead2/><ref name=dead3/>隨後巴格達迪的屍體由美方秘密[[海葬|海葬]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://amp.rfi.fr/cn/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85/20191029-%E7%BE%8E%E5%86%9B%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%B7%B2%E6%B5%B7%E8%91%ACis%E5%A4%B4%E7%9B%AE%E5%B7%B4%E6%A0%BC%E8%BE%BE%E8%BF%AA |title=美国军方表示已对巴格达迪遗体进行海葬 |access-date=2019-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191029230519/https://amp.rfi.fr/cn/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85/20191029-%E7%BE%8E%E5%86%9B%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%B7%B2%E6%B5%B7%E8%91%ACis%E5%A4%B4%E7%9B%AE%E5%B7%B4%E6%A0%BC%E8%BE%BE%E8%BF%AA |archive-date=2019-10-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而有聯合國高階官員表示因缺乏證據仍無法確認巴格達迪的死訊<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20191030000003-260408?chdtv |title=“巴格達迪真死了？UN官員：只見川普一張嘴 |publisher=中時電子報 |date=2019-10-30 |access-date=2019-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191030160100/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20191030000003-260408?chdtv |archive-date=2019-10-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月31日，伊斯蘭國發佈錄音證實其死訊，並揚言向美國及所有背叛者報復<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.takungpao.com.hk/international/text/2019/1101/368516.html |title=ISIS證巴格達迪已死 揚言報復美國 |publisher=大公報 |date=2019-11-01 |accessdate=2019-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101094730/http://www.takungpao.com.hk/international/text/2019/1101/368516.html |archive-date=2019-11-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同時巴格達迪至少十位以上家屬被土耳其方面抓獲<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sputniknews.cn/amp/politics/201911071030005282/ |title=土耳其总统：土耳其拘留的巴格达迪亲属人数已达两位数 |access-date=2019-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107104530/http://sputniknews.cn/amp/politics/201911071030005282/ |archive-date=2019-11-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。關在敘利亞戰俘營中的伊斯蘭國被俘人員對於巴格達迪的死訊分成兩種不同反應：一部份對哈里發國早已幻滅的「前任聖戰士」紛紛唱跳狂歡、詛咒巴格達迪「終於要下地獄」；但另一部分死忠從眾則沈默地不發一語，還有些人堅持不願相信「異教徒的假新聞」。<ref>{{Cite web|title=巴格達迪自爆死！川普證實：ISIS首腦在敘利亞遭美軍擊殺|url=https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8662/4129236|accessdate=2020-08-19|last=聯合新聞網|work=轉角國際 udn Global|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2020-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325061621/https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8662/4129236|dead-url=no}}</ref>

